
  Dragalge    Poison Type Pokémon

  Their poison is strong enough 
  to eat through the hull of a 
  tanker, and they spit it indiscriminately 
  at anything that enters their 
  territory. 
	Evolution Chain
      Skrelp ► Dragalge

